<https://omc.co/5511993891773/749/entidade/Regra_Artigo124_Reserva> <https://omc.co/vocabulary/descricao> "Reserva prévia de espaço comum via Portal WEB do Condomínio."@pt <https://omc.co/graph/5511993891773> .
